 Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be bereft of,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φίλης αἰῶνος ἀμερθῇς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:58\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.58</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐδέ τι δαιτὸς ἀμέρδεαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:21:290\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.290</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ ἧπαρ τῆς ἐκροῆς ἀμερθέν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0719.tlg003.perseus-grc1:2:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aret.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ CA\">CA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.6</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2571.tlg001:24p.470M\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hierocl.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">in CA</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24p.470M.</biblScope> </bibl>: rarely c. acc. rei, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἂν . . καρπὸν ἀμερθῶσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:9:8:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HP\">HP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.8.2</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n5160.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. pers. only, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bereave of natural rights,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"gr